LineOfDialogue.responderLine: %random(Oh geeze... please move.,Ah! You're in my bubble!,Why are you moving like that? What are you doing?,Gah! Get away from me!,Are you just gonna stand there with that look on your face?)%

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: ...can I have some of your %rand(hair,receipts,gum,toenail clippings)%?
I have a collection.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Get the freak away from me.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %rand(Boo!,Hey!,How ya doin?)%
Did I get you? I got you, didn't I!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: %rand(... please go away., ... so not cool., ... can't you just say hi like a normal person!?!)%

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Ha ha ha! That's really funny!
HA HA HA!
Aha ha ha ha! Ha ha!
Hey %r%, do you ever play any RPGs?
Oh man, I bet you would make a really good %rand(paladin,ranger,wizard,bard,fighter/rogue/cleric,fighter/mage)%! Like, I could totally picture you as one.
I had one once. Yeah. Really cool character. Yeah. C'mon, you should play!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Maybe if I was a %pejorative%. Which I'm not.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %r%, I can totally see you playing an epic %random(barbarian,barbarian/mage,cloudmancer,dragonstrider,lava troll)% in my tabletop roleplaying campaign!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Really? Actually, I already play one.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Really? What edition?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Eight, obviously. With the %random(new Luxembourg,Open Qualifiers,stripped Euclidean,Burnished French)% addendums, of course.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: All right, fine. I guess you're not just bluffing.
Hey %r%.
'Ph'nglui Mglw'nafh Cthulhu R'lyeh wgah'nagl fhtagn!'

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Huh? How did you even say that?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %r%.
'Ph'nglui Mglw'nafh Cthulhu R'lyeh wgah'nagl fhtagn!'

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Huh? How did you even say that?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Shhhhh! I can't hear them when you're talking!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Errrr... OK. Maybe I'll talk to you... later.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %r%, do you know much about %toc1%s?
Oh, really? I love %toc1%s! I just can't get enough %toc1%s.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Ew! So you're stupid and gross, too.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hi there! Have you met my friend %gender(i,Mr,Ms)%. Handy? Say 'hi' Handy!
Hey %r%! Did you know I collect.... %toc1%s?
You wanna see my collection some time?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I'd love to! I can bring my collection over, too!

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: We can compare!
%greeting% %r%.
Hey %r%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Ummm, hey. What do you want?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hello %r%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: This is getting old. Go away or shut up.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Greetings, %r%.
Hey %r%. Are we having que-sa-dilas for lunch?
What are you talking about?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I'm talking about 'quesadillas'. You know, the food with tortillas and cheese?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: You mean tortilas?

LineOfDialogue.otherLine: I don't know what you are talking about.
I mean, I've heard of que-sa-dilas, not whatever you just said.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Whatever, you guys are just weird.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: I feel weird today, %r%.
You know how sometimes, in life, a creepy clown comes up to you, and smiles?
And then the clown gets like this weird smirk and it suddenly seems to get much colder and there's like this wind blowing even though the grass isn't waving?
And then later that night you hear weird noises almost like a clown breathing coming from outside your bedroom door, and in the morning there's a single clown nose at the foot of your bed?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I totally know what you mean, %i%.
But when life gives you lemons, make lemonade!

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Uh.... yeah. Thanks for the advice I guess.
Hey %r%.
Did you hear about when %toc1%?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Uhh, yeah. That was pretty gross. You're never going to live that down.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Eh, it wasn't so bad. I'd totally do it again.
What, you wouldn't like to join in?
%greeting% %r%.
Have you ever felt like just doing something weird?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I guess at some point in my life, sure?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: I just mean, sometimes I just like to stand near people and watch them awkwardly.
Like this...

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Well, we all have our own ways of spending time, you just shouldn't do it that often.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: So... you're not weirded out?

Hey %r%! Did you know I %random(collect cereal boxes,am a huge fan of Stone Age era plant life,like to get my hair cut once a week,have a bunch of identical outfits so I can dress like this every day,have the phone numbers of my friends and family memorized instead of just in my phone's address book,am allergic to sweaters,hate tomatoes but love ketchup,have never read Moby-Dick)%?
Isn't that *weird*?
